description: All you need from one USB port!The Etekcity Docking Station is a great way to expand the connectivity of your PC. This hub offers 6 USB ports and one of the 2 USB 3.0 has Fast Charging function when PC on Sleeping Mode, HDMI and DVI output, and one Gigabit Ethernet port! Easily-accessible USB and video ports eliminate the hassle of connecting/disconnecting peripherals in hard-to-reach areas.HD video, super-speed USB, and lightning-fast ethernet!With the HDMI and DVI with VGA adapter video ports, your computer can be connected to two additional monitors, HDTVs or projectors at up to 2048x1152px HD resolution. The connected monitor can be configured to mirror/extend your Windows Mac desktop.RequirementProcessor: 2.0GHz Core2Duo or better RAM: 1GBWindows: XP (32-bit only) SP3/Vista/7/8 SupportedNote: 64-bit Editions of XP and Windows Server Editions are not supported.MAC OS X: Download the newest driver recommendedLinux: Display link provides open source library. Driver is community written. Displaylink.org has details for advanced and adventurous usersSpecificationsUSB 3.0 transfer rate up to 5Gbps (2 ports)USB 2.0 transfer rate up to 480Mbps (4 ports)Ports: DVI / HDMI / RJ45 / USB2.0 / USB3.02 additional video ports with maximum resolution: 2048x1152px Hdmi and DVIBackwards compatible with USB 2.0Power input: 5VEthernet network: 1000Mbps/100Mbps/10MbpsAudio input/outputPackage includes1x Etekcity USB 3.0 Universal Docking Station1x USB 3.0 cable1x DVI to VGA Adapter1x DC 12V/2A Power adapter1x CD Driver1x User's manual (English/Chinese)Note: Horizontal Base Mount not included
title: Etekcity® Ultimate USB 3.0 Universal Laptop Docking Station with Dual Video Outputs for Windows 8.1, 8, 7, XP Even with Mac - DisplayLink HDMI & DVI/VGA up to 2048x1152, 2 USB 3.0 Ports, 4 USB 2.0 Ports, Gigabit Ethernet, Audio, AC 12V/2A Power Adapter Included
